rows.label: xs33500100_MSG0010
rows.name:
It's you two! I was so worried about you!
What a relief...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33500100_MSG0020
rows.name:
We finally found friends!
Tatsu and Linly were searching everywhere![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33500100_MSG0025
rows.name: I'm happy to see you're both all right as well.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33500100_MSG0027
rows.name:
We're going back, right?
To face Void again.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33500100_MSG0035
rows.name: Before that, I wanted to say...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33500100_MSG0063
rows.name: It looks like some kinda relic, doesn't it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33500100_MSG0064
rows.name: It's a pretty big structure to put in a place like this...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33500100_MSG0065
rows.name: I can't imagine that it was put here just for decoration.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33500100_MSG0068
rows.name: Right. I was thinking that as well.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33500100_MSG0070
rows.name:
Tatsu also have big curious.
Would not say no to sightseeing detour![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33500100_MSG0090
rows.name: Yeah, info is our top priority right now.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33500100_MSG0100
rows.name: We should at least check it out.[ST:wait ]
